{"tid":1603490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十月一號全世界要入港島啊！唔要遍地開花！","createTime":"2019-09-29T16:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T18:09:48.000Z","uid":30283,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4dab4b9c2fb1bb1b2bcf5faee09590a6fa8c7751","tid":1603490,"uid":30283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"記唔記得十月一號我地係出黎幫中共慶佢老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地越分散，敵人就越容易粉飾太平！你地諗下8月5號果日我地又係分散哂係各區，結果就係根本聚焦唔到落去有幾多人參與左三罷！<br />\n<br />\n我地依家係要話比全世界知，香港大多數人都憎撚死中共！憎撚死雜種！大部份香港人都已經唔撚覺得香港仲有咩一國兩制！十月一號係最好機會去宣揚呢個信息出去比全世界人知！所以我地一定要集中去哂一個地方！逼撚爆港島！甘先可以為我地所有既行動，仲有外國所有制裁行動，提供穩固既民意基礎！<br />\n<br />\n香港人！加油！"},{"pid":"9e6812806dcb737a84b965faf8b941a737d5b547","tid":1603490,"uid":30283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:40:10.000Z","msg":"自推十次！"},{"pid":"94bad49e7d404f8df13b2cd8ffe6bd39e49c898c","tid":1603490,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05af280fc2c0dee4236c40b24e5c5811e5532c94","tid":1603490,"uid":249721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:41:11.000Z","msg":"經過今日仲話唔開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢文勿推"},{"pid":"bea92cf973c6de9231d4fda1e5ce7de6cfb02078","tid":1603490,"uid":245201,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:41:34.000Z","msg":"強烈支持！<br />\n終於可以一次過捉晒你班陷家剷，一天都光晒！"},{"pid":"8f5e34c0b63d9f9ecc1073aa05f5d80debd3841d","tid":1603490,"uid":51338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:42:09.000Z","msg":"尋日公佈六區開花<br />\n今日929重兵<br />\n<br />\n鬼黎<br />\n<br />\n不推文pls"},{"pid":"259987383dc4728d900a20e6d8a2715aa17b1839","tid":1603490,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X0LcvJe.j